<li id="cite_note-16"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Cold_War#cite_ref-16">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation news"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.britannica.com/topic/Left-Communist">"Left Communist | Russian political faction"</a>. <i>Encyclopedia Britannica</i><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">30 September</span> 2018</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Encyclopedia+Britannica&amp;rft.atitle=Left+Communist+%7C+Russian+political+faction&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.britannica.com%2Ftopic%2FLeft-Communist&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACold+War" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/></span>
